  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Monopoly is a PlayStation video game based on the board game Monopoly, released on November 6, 1997 in Europe. Developed by Gremlin Interactive and published by Hasbro Interactive, this title was one of many inspired by the property. Despite using the same box art as the 1995 PC version of Monopoly, it is not the same game.",
